# Re-Anime

<strong> Wanna download anime of your desired formats with fast downloading speed and having subbed/dubbed options? </strong>

</br>well you are at the right place!!

## Features
![alt text](https://github.com/varunpanchal283/Re-Anime/blob/main/img/reanime.png?raw=true)
- Beautiful command line interface to interact with re-anime where you have got lots of options to choose.
- A search engine where u can have a list of desired anime you want.
- A Download-Manager which can maximize your download speed.

## Requirements

- It's a standalone tool, it doesn't need any external requirements except pypi packages.
- To install this project run `pip install re-anime` 

## Usage

- `-download` || `-d` will download you anime. `-d https://gogoanime.vc/category/edens-zero` to download whole anime | `-d https://gogoanime.vc/edens-zero-episode-6` to download an episode
- `-ep` will allow you to specify episodes. `-ep 1,5` to download episodes 1 and 5 | `-ep 1-5` to download episodes from 1 to 5.
- `-res` will allow you to specify resolutions. `-res 1080` | `-res 720` | `-res 480`.
- `-dir` will allow you to specify download directory. `-dir E://Downloads`.
- `-thread` if you have a good internet connection of 100MBPS or more, than you can give thread values as 50 to 100 to speedup downloads
- `-changedir` if you want to permenantly change the default download directory

## CLI Command

- `re-anime -d <URL> -ep [1,2-10] -dir /content/path -res 1080|720|480 -thread 100`
- `re-anime -changedir <PATH>`

## Provider

- gogoanime.vc | gogoanime.ai
- gogo-play.net
- gogo-stream.com


